**Bottlenecks**
- Render-blocking CSS + synchronous JS (no `async`/`defer`)
- No code splitting → all JS downloaded/parsed upfront
- No image optimization → 478 KB PNG icon
- Service Worker cache-first but no API response caching → stale data
- Long tasks: order rendering (~100 ms), map init (~150 ms)

**Recommendations**
- Optimize iconsize + formats (WebP, AVIF)
- Minify CSS/JS; enable gzip/Brotli
- Add `async`/`defer` to non-critical scripts
- Implement code splitting (dynamic imports for sections)
- Lazy-load map tiles & offscreen images
- Cache API responses with stale-while-revalidate

